> show dbs
amazeriffic  0.078GB
chuchu       0.078GB
local        0.078GB
test         0.078GB
tutu         0.078GB

...
> db.scores.insert([{name: "Antonio", cal: 5}, {name: "Nayla", cal: 6}])
> db.scores.find({})
{ "_id" : ObjectId("57150162224028006668b655"), "name" : "Juana", "cal" : 10 }
